                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-320-off1837 t18200918-320-cd1838"></join>, one purse, value 1 d. and 13 s. in monies numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-320-victim2899" type="victimName">
                           Peter 
                           Croiley
                        <interp inst="t18200918-320-victim2899" type="surname" value="Croiley"></interp>
